I knew that I would fall for him the first time he took my hand in his

in that touch
of his fingertips
with his palm pressed against mine
my heart raced
my legs quivered
my knees nearly gave way 
and he proved himself to be
not only a gentleman
but thief
stealing away my breath
in that moment
of breathless bliss
I knew
and became no longer my own
but his

Midnight musings by:
Tammi Brown 
2018
